title: Grateful Dead Live at Miami Arena on 1989-10-25
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Just A Little Light, Friend Of The Devil, Stuck Inside Of Mobile With The Memphis Blues Again, Cold Rain & Snow, Picasso Moon, Deal

Set 2

Playing In The Band > Uncle John's Band > Playing In The Band Reprise
Standing On The Moon > Truckin' > Drums > Space > Gimme Some Lovin' > Wharf Rat > Sugar Magnolia > Sunshine Daydream

Encore:
U.S. Blues

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
